ood gunplay\n - Immediate access to some guns\n - Sidearm camera, hand grenades\n - Full practice range\n - 2 shoot-house assessments\n - Some challenges and modes\n - Hidden cashwads to find\n - Attachments to unlock and buy\n - Balloon Stabber minigame\n - Home hub area\n - 35 ridiculous announcements\n - A secret demo area to discover!\n\nTECHNICAL FEATURES\n\n - 90hz refresh rate (Quest 2+)\n - Full roomscale support\n - Seated play support\n - Left handed support\n - Captions\n - Locomotion options\n - Solo / offline\n\nFULL GAME FEATURES (NOT IN DEMO)\n\n - All 8 shoot-house assessments\n - Full challenge board\n - Full access to all modes\n - Full arsenal of 20+ firearms\n - Kamikaze drones\n - Augmented visor\n - Even more Tactical Tools\n - Both minigame floors\n - SimpleJack arcade cabinet\n - Facility induction\n - Progression system\n - Functional grievance booth\n - Big secret area, beyond the booth\n - More story / lore to uncover\n - Full 120 random announcements\n - Multiple save slots\n - Difficulty options\n - Permadeath option\n - New game plus\n - And even more!\n\nLooking for a tactical room clearing sim? A fast-paced action shooter? A casual, unusual, indie-game to explore? Shotwood has you covered! Grab this FREE demo right now and... SHOOT SOME WOOD!", "short_description": "FREE vertical slice demo of Shotwood. Smash deadly wooden targets with realistic firearms & explosives while you try to escape from this ominous, ridiculous, mysterious facility. Shotwood is the casual (yet satisfyingly tactical) shoot-house themed game!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/terms.html", "publisher_name": "Concrete Box", "support_website_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/support.html", "website_url": "https://www.concretebox.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326